              <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Prevents influenza infection:</strong> Reduces the risk of getting sick with the flu.</li>
              <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Reduces severity:</strong> Even if you get the flu, the vaccine can reduce the severity of symptoms.</li>
              <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Protects vulnerable populations:</strong> Especially important for infants, seniors, and people with chronic diseases.</li>
              <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Helps reduce hospitalizations:</strong> Decreases the risk of severe complications and flu-related hospital stays.</li>
            </ul>
