              <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Annual dose:</strong> One dose every year, as the virus changes annually.</li>
              <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Children (6 months–8 years):</strong> May need 2 doses during their first year of vaccination, spaced at least 4 weeks apart.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
